Who was the informant?

11
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,710
Did I bring up a difficult subject?

12
00:02:55,979 --> 00:02:57,520
What I'm asking is who tipped off
about the knife...

13
00:02:57,949 --> 00:03:01,050
