You wanted me to ride with you
to ask this question.

15
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:07,930
Prosecutor Cha, I hope you can
answer my question quickly.

16
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,560
It was an anonymous informant.

17
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:14,300
