piece of evidence.

25
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,680
Cha Yoo Jung.

26
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:34,189
Whatever. I can't hear a word
you are saying right now.

27
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:37,060
To get the warrant, I put my job
on the line and searched his house.

28
00:03:37,490 --> 00:03:38,789
But this is what has happened.

29
00:03:39,419 --> 00:03:42,159
I'm in a tight spot now, Ji Wook.

30
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,560
I...

31
00:03:47,099 --> 00:03:48,099
Yes?

32
00:03:51,139 --> 00:03:52,139
What?

33
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:55,009
Okay. I'm on my way now.

34
00:03:58,479 --> 00:04:00,240
I really saw it.

35
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:02,009
- Are you sure?
- Hey, punk.

36
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:04,580
Do you think I only
see hallucinations?

37
00:04:05,419 --> 00:04:07,620
Mr. Bang, Mr. Bang.

38
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:09,550
Mr. Bang...

39
00:04:11,990 --> 00:04:13,020
What is this?

40
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:16,560
You said his finger moved.

41
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,129
That's what I wanted to say.

42
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:20,970
What did the doctor say?

43
00:04:21,899 --> 00:04:23,399
Well, the doctor...

44
00:04:24,069 --> 00:04:26,540
said that I might have
been mistaken.

45
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:32,779
He really moved. Listen to me.

46
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,879
His finger...

47
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:36,480
Hey! It moved again! Look!

48
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,019
Look! It moved!

49
00:04:46,459 --> 00:04:49,589
Hey, just wait a bit more. Okay?

50
00:04:49,589 --> 00:04:52,730
His finger is going to move again.
Keep looking. My goodness.

51
00:05:02,110 --> 00:05:03,410
It really moved.

52
00:05:04,209 --> 00:05:05,209
Mr. Byun.

53
00:05:06,709 --> 00:05:07,779
Take a seat.

54
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:09,250
You should get some sleep.

55
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:12,720
Goodness.

56
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:16,050
(Gookil Hospital)

57
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:50,990
No, no way. That can't be.

58
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,120
Pardon?

59
00:05:52,490 --> 00:05:54,029
- What?
- What did you say?

60
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,389
I didn't say anything.

61
00:06:00,529 --> 00:06:03,000
If you are behind this, Eun Hyuk,
I'm going to...

