I always wondered
when we are going to be friendly.

67
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,120
Is today the day?

68
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:22,120
Are we going to hold hands today?

69
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,160
How dare you.

70
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:32,730
We all know that all of us
are not in a good mood.

71
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:36,730
But we must still smile. That's how
good things will come to our way.

72
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:38,970
That's right.

73
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:45,110
Eun Hyuk, it's been a while since
you said something that made sense.

74
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:48,850
He's right. We must stay positive
for the good fortune to come...

75
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:51,850
and that's how Mr. Bang
will wake up as well.

76
00:06:51,850 --> 00:06:53,750
- You think so too, right?
- Of course.

77
00:06:54,819 --> 00:06:57,290
Well, I agree with you guys on that.

78
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:18,009
I need to tell you something
about Jung Hyun Soo.

79
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:21,079
Did he do something again?

80
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:25,879
- Well, that's...
- Ji Wook.

81
00:07:33,589 --> 00:07:34,629
Mr. Bang.

82
00:07:35,329 --> 00:07:36,889
Mr. Bang, are you awake now?

83
00:07:36,889 --> 00:07:39,360
Can you see me? It's me, Ji Wook.

84
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,430
Ji Wook.

85
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:42,329
Yes, that's right. It's me, Ji Wook.

86
00:07:47,339 --> 00:07:49,069
Mr. Bang.

87
00:07:49,139 --> 00:07:52,040
Mr. Bang, it's me, Eun Hyuk.
Can you recognize me?

88
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,279
Of course, I can.

89
00:07:55,610 --> 00:07:56,750
Eun Hyuk.

90
00:07:57,050 --> 00:07:58,079
Hey.

91
00:07:58,949 --> 00:08:02,050
Hey, what about me?
Do you recognize me?

92
00:08:02,149 --> 00:08:03,649
Mr. Bang, it's me!

93
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:05,689
- Young Hee.
- That's me!

94
00:08:05,689 --> 00:08:08,730
My name is Young Hee. I'm Young Hee!

95
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:12,600
My goodness. But how dare you
speak to me informally? You jerk.

96
00:08:12,829 --> 00:08:16,199
Gosh, I'm so happy that you're
awake.

97
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:18,540
Good job. Good job for waking up.

98
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:21,240
My gosh. I'm so proud of you,
Eun Ho.

99
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,839
My gosh, I can't believe this.

100
00:08:23,269 --> 00:08:24,740
My goodness.

101
00:08:24,810 --> 00:08:27,449
See? What did I tell you?

102
00:08:27,509 --> 00:08:28,680
I told you so.

103
00:08:28,850 --> 00:08:30,680
Wait here. I'll call the doctor.

104
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:41,330
Thank you. Thank you so much,
Mr. Bang.

105
00:08:41,830 --> 00:08:42,929
Thank you.

106
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,870
I'm so relieved.

107
00:08:54,809 --> 00:08:58,440
My... My gosh, you startled me.

108
00:08:59,179 --> 00:09:00,240
It's okay.

109
00:09:00,909 --> 00:09:02,909
(The Memory of That Day)

110
00:09:02,909 --> 00:09:03,919
I'm so relieved.

