Yes, we found the car.

139
00:10:49,649 --> 00:10:51,659
But the driver has disappeared.

140
00:10:52,889 --> 00:10:54,059
What did the doctor say?

141
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:57,429
I don't know. Apparently, his head
