beg me to work there.

152
00:11:35,899 --> 00:11:37,399
Prosecutor Cha, wait.

153
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,000
I have something for you.

154
00:11:42,669 --> 00:11:43,669
Mr. Bang got this list...

155
00:11:43,669 --> 00:11:46,340
