00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:08,529
Yes. The most suspicious person
is on the top of the list.

166
00:12:08,669 --> 00:12:10,970
I actually met him in person.

167
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:15,809
Okay. I'll look into these people.

168
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:35,129
I had...

169
00:12:37,129 --> 00:12:38,360
