so many things.

171
00:12:42,570 --> 00:12:44,970
I was going to make sure
that you'd get...

172
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:48,240
punished by law.

173
00:13:14,799 --> 00:13:16,370
I'm sure it was Jung Hyun Soo,

174
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:18,070
but I wasn't able to see his face
directly...

175
