334
00:23:39,190 --> 00:23:41,420
I'll clean it up. I'll...

335
00:23:42,329 --> 00:23:43,329
What was that about?

336
00:23:43,329 --> 00:23:45,329
Goodness. You should clean it up,
Mr. No.

337
00:23:45,329 --> 00:23:46,599
Hey, you clean this up!

338
00:23:46,599 --> 00:23:47,799
What's the matter with him?

339
00:23:48,599 --> 00:23:49,930
Congratulations!

