346
00:24:08,890 --> 00:24:11,150
Speaking of which, people there...

347
00:24:11,490 --> 00:24:15,289
always make sure to strictly punish
companies in such cases.

348
00:24:16,329 --> 00:24:19,500
I'll tell you what happened
when I first went to the US.

349
00:24:19,859 --> 00:24:22,799
My wife used to be very pretty.

350
00:24:22,930 --> 00:24:25,470
Some blond jerks
started hitting on her,

351
00:24:25,470 --> 00:24:28,440
calling her a pretty girl
or a cutie.

352
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:30,009
Gosh, here he goes again.

353
00:24:31,210 --> 00:24:33,509
What? What did you just say?

354
00:24:34,309 --> 00:24:35,650
Nothing. I didn't say anything.

355
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,380
I should put up with it.
He's the father.

356
00:24:37,549 --> 00:24:39,450
I'm not your father.

357
00:24:40,349 --> 00:24:43,789
I didn't say you're my father.
You have great hearing.

358
00:24:45,519 --> 00:24:46,519
Get her out of here.

359
00:24:46,519 --> 00:24:48,430
Gosh! It's a complete mess here!

360
00:24:49,259 --> 00:24:50,990
