363
00:24:57,529 --> 00:24:59,170
Please go ahead, Mr. Bang.

364
00:25:00,069 --> 00:25:01,569
It's actually not about work.

365
00:25:02,339 --> 00:25:04,009
Something seems a bit off to me.

366
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:09,549
Shall I say we're missing some
things that are supposed to be here?

367
00:25:10,549 --> 00:25:12,920
As you know, I was in a coma.

368
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:17,150
Oh, that's right. Did you have
an out-of-body experience?

369
00:25:17,220 --> 00:25:18,789
I heard it happens to some people.

370
00:25:18,890 --> 00:25:21,559
I heard some people
go to the underworld and come back.

371
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:22,759
Gosh, are you serious?

372
00:25:23,059 --> 00:25:24,160
Bong Hee.

373
00:25:24,660 --> 00:25:26,329
I hope you end up in the fiery pit.

374
00:25:29,930 --> 00:25:31,200
I didn't experience any of that.

375
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:36,410
But I think I had some dreams.

376
00:25:39,210 --> 00:25:41,309
I remember a few of them.

377
00:25:42,410 --> 00:25:45,549
Wake up already, will you?

378
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:50,519
If you wake up, I'll donate
all of my assets.

379
00:25:51,390 --> 00:25:54,819
No, let me correct that.
I'll give them all to you.

380
00:25:54,819 --> 00:25:56,829
You can have it all, okay?

381
00:25:57,130 --> 00:25:58,829
I'll even change the name
of our firm.

382
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:02,599
I'll take out my surname
and include yours.

383
00:26:03,529 --> 00:26:05,339
"No, Ji, and Bang".

384
00:26:05,839 --> 00:26:07,400
I remember it vividly.

385
00:26:09,740 --> 00:26:11,779
I never said such a thing.

386
00:26:15,309 --> 00:26:18,650
If you ever lose the ladder game,
I'll serve your penalty for you.

387
00:26:19,220 --> 00:26:21,579
You can count on me
every single time.

388
00:26:22,650 --> 00:26:24,960
So please wake up, okay?

389
00:26:32,359 --> 00:26:33,460
Mr. Bang.

390
00:26:35,029 --> 00:26:36,799
Please wake up already.

391
00:26:37,730 --> 00:26:40,839
Why did you have to end up like this
after working so hard?

392
00:26:41,369 --> 00:26:43,009
Please just wake up.

393
00:26:43,240 --> 00:26:47,180
Then I'll hire an office manager
as well as a secretary for you.

394
00:26:47,539 --> 00:26:51,150
You can have your own
secretary and driver.

395
00:26:52,220 --> 00:26:55,349
I earn a lot of money, you know.
