396
00:27:00,319 --> 00:27:03,559
What a fun, imaginative dream.

397
00:27:03,559 --> 00:27:05,400
Gosh. Oh, my!

398
00:27:28,420 --> 00:27:30,549
Oh, right. Mr. Bang's medication.

399
00:27:33,490 --> 00:27:36,529
If I pass by a pharmacy, remind me
to pick up Mr. Bang's medication.

400
00:27:40,059 --> 00:27:41,200
(Searching)

401
00:27:43,930 --> 00:27:45,769
(Under the Tree Pharmacy)

402
00:27:46,069 --> 00:27:47,099
(Directions)

403
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:57,650
I've forgotten about it,
but who could it have been?

404
00:27:58,420 --> 00:28:00,849
The person who left
the knife at Jung Hyun Soo's house.

405
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:04,319
Gosh. Then...

406
00:28:05,319 --> 00:28:07,490
the culprit must be one of them...

407
00:28:07,490 --> 00:28:08,490
Culprit of what?

408
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:17,329
I've been reading...

409
00:28:18,230 --> 00:28:21,400
