I decided not to use that evidence.

419
00:29:31,339 --> 00:29:32,339
But...

420
00:29:33,839 --> 00:29:37,480
I don't know if I have made
the right choice or not.

421
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:41,119
He's definitely the culprit.

422
00:29:41,619 --> 00:29:43,819
He even admitted the crimes himself.

423
00:29:45,220 --> 00:29:46,220
But...

424
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:48,559
I'm pretending to be better...

425
00:29:48,630 --> 00:29:50,230
