00:31:48,339 --> 00:31:50,180
You're aware of it, right?

439
00:31:50,180 --> 00:31:51,180
Yes, I am.

440
00:31:51,980 --> 00:31:53,819
I've already told the police
everything.

441
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:58,150
