450
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,480
That's correct.

451
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:25,180
What did you just say?

452
00:32:28,279 --> 00:32:29,349
We, at the prosecution,

453
00:32:29,720 --> 00:32:32,660
