the people's trust.

456
00:32:39,559 --> 00:32:40,559
Do you understand?

457
00:32:44,670 --> 00:32:46,970
How have you been, Mr. Kang?

458
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:50,509
Not bad, thanks to you.

459
00:32:51,710 --> 00:32:54,240
Why are you thanking me?
You're locked up here because of me.

460
