because of me.

462
00:33:02,490 --> 00:33:03,990
Why would you want me
to defend you again?

463
00:33:03,990 --> 00:33:05,089
You're the only one...

464
00:33:05,819 --> 00:33:07,390
I can count on.

465
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,730
I...

466
00:33:10,559 --> 00:33:12,299
