being falsely accused like this.

467
00:33:13,099 --> 00:33:16,000
I never started any fire.

468
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:18,700
So please...

469
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,940
help me just this once.

470
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:23,240
Please?

471
00:33:24,569 --> 00:33:25,579
Please...

472
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:33,019
Two years ago, Kang Sun Il...

473
00:33:33,019 --> 00:33:35,789
was arrested as the culprit
of the Doboo-dong arson case.

474
00:33:36,089 --> 00:33:37,089
The victim was...

475
00:33:38,650 --> 00:33:39,660
this man.

476
00:33:39,789 --> 00:33:41,819
His name is Chae Sung Woo,
and he was sleeping at home.

477
00:33:41,819 --> 00:33:43,359
He suffocated to death
immediately at the scene.

478
00:33:43,359 --> 00:33:46,660
Kang Sun Il was sentenced to 10
years in prison at his first trial.

479
00:33:46,859 --> 00:33:47,859
