480
00:33:47,859 --> 00:33:50,430
The prosecution insisted
that it's a revenge crime.

481
00:33:50,769 --> 00:33:54,200
Kang Sun Il's daughter got hit
by Chae Sung Woo's car and died.

482
00:33:54,299 --> 00:33:56,470
Chae Sung Woo, who was drunk
and didn't have a driver's license,

483
00:33:56,769 --> 00:33:59,579
