484
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,680
Goodness.

485
00:34:02,079 --> 00:34:03,779
From the forensics report alone,

486
00:34:03,779 --> 00:34:06,849
I don't think it can be concluded
that Kang Sun Il...

487
00:34:06,849 --> 00:34:08,519
is the arsonist.

488
00:34:08,949 --> 00:34:09,949
I know, right?

489
00:34:10,420 --> 00:34:12,989
The incompetent attorney
who lost that first trial...

490
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:14,619
was me.

491
00:34:15,090 --> 00:34:17,559
He appealed, and the trial
for that will take place soon.

492
00:34:17,730 --> 00:34:19,829
He wants me
to defend him once again.

493
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:20,960
But...

494
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:23,070
I've already lost once,

495
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:25,269
so I'm feeling unsure
and not confident.

496
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,639
Hence, I'm asking you guys for help.

497
00:34:26,869 --> 00:34:28,500
Ji Wook, help me out.

498
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:30,409
Ms. Eun and Mr. Bang,
please help me with this.

499
00:34:32,010 --> 00:34:33,010
