you begged me not to help you.

502
00:34:40,179 --> 00:34:41,480
Okay. Then don't help me.

503
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,719
All right, I won't.

504
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:45,050
You should offer help
if I tell you not to help me.

505
00:34:45,719 --> 00:34:47,389
He doesn't seem so bright, does he?

506
00:34:47,460 --> 00:34:48,489
No, not really.

507
00:34:48,489 --> 00:34:50,489
