509
00:34:51,489 --> 00:34:54,099
I really think Kang Sun Il
is innocent. I'm serious.

510
00:34:54,099 --> 00:34:55,099
With Jung Hyun Soo,

511
00:34:58,099 --> 00:34:59,539
we thought the same.

512
00:35:02,769 --> 00:35:03,769
And...

513
00:35:05,909 --> 00:35:06,909
I'm sorry,

514
00:35:08,909 --> 00:35:10,280
but I don't want to work on...

515
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:15,489
arson cases.

516
